through the crowdfunding website Patreon.

236
00:09:31,450 --> 00:09:33,510
carbide149 asks:

237
00:09:33,510 --> 00:09:36,990
“If Chinese citizens are able to travel
abroad,

238
00:09:36,990 --> 00:09:38,879
what is stopping them from learning the truth
about

239
00:09:38,879 --> 00:09:41,670
the atrocities the CCP is covering up

240
00:09:41,670 --> 00:09:44,089
such as the Tiananmen Square Massacre?

241
00:09:44,089 --> 00:09:46,380
Nothing is technically stopping them.

242
00:09:46,380 --> 00:09:48,899
And a lot of them do learn some shocking things

243
00:09:48,899 --> 00:09:51,019
when they travel to free countries.

244
00:09:51,019 --> 00:09:52,709
Except that the Communist Party

245
00:09:52,709 --> 00:09:55,839
has done such an excellent job of brainwashing
people

246
00:09:55,839 --> 00:09:59,570
that even when some mainland Chinese citizens
travel abroad,

247
00:09:59,570 --> 00:10:02,809
they reject the truth even after seeing it
on TV,

248
00:10:02,809 --> 00:10:04,279
or being handed a flyer,

249
00:10:04,279 --> 00:10:05,899
or talking to foreigners.

250
00:10:05,899 --> 00:10:07,059
A lot of times,

251
00:10:07,059 --> 00:10:10,490
when people encounter criticism of the Chinese
Communist Party,

252
00:10:10,490 --> 00:10:13,550
they conflate that with criticism of *China*—

253
00:10:13,550 --> 00:10:14,660
their country—

254
00:10:14,660 --> 00:10:15,949
so they reject it.

255
00:10:15,949 --> 00:10:18,209
Like they take it personally.

256
00:10:18,209 --> 00:10:20,930
Or they learn about the Tiananmen Square Massacre,

257
00:10:20,930 --> 00:10:22,040
but they think, oh,

258
00:10:22,040 --> 00:10:24,119
well it happened a long time ago,

259
00:10:24,119 --> 00:10:27,629
and the students were also agitating the situation.

260
00:10:27,629 --> 00:10:30,410
It often takes a long time for them to realize
that

261
00:10:30,410 --> 00:10:33,089
they’ve been lied to their whole lives.

262
00:10:33,089 --> 00:10:36,439
And nearly all Chinese language media outside
China

263
00:10:36,439 --> 00:10:39,160
are controlled through either Communist Party
